'''里斯·奧斯科特'''（{{lang-en|'''Reece Oxford'''}}，{{bd|1998年|12月16日|catIdx=Oxford, Reece}}）是一名[[英格蘭|英格蘭]]職業足球員，司職[[後衛_(足球)|中堅]]，現效力於[[德甲|德甲]]球隊[[奥格斯堡足球俱乐部|奥格斯堡]]。奧斯科特於16歲198日為韋斯咸首次上陣，使他成為球會有史以來最年輕的球員，擊敗了比利·威廉斯於1922年建立為韋斯咸在16歲221天首次上陣的記錄<ref>{{cite web|url=https://twitter.com/whufc_official/status/616265083187036160|title=West Ham United FC on Twitter|work=Twitter|accessdate=2 July 2015|archive-date=2019-06-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190630195458/https://twitter.com/WestHamUtd/status/616265083187036160|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://twitter.com/whufc_official/status/616265561752911872|title=West Ham United FC on Twitter|work=Twitter|accessdate=2 July 2015|archive-date=2019-12-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191214132846/https://twitter.com/whufc_official/status/616265561752911872|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

==球員生涯==
奧斯科特在2014-15賽季與韋斯咸正選球員一同操練，但是主要是為球會的U21隊出戰。儘管他是最年輕的球員，他在一些場合亦會出任隊長。2014年8月27日，他以15歲之齡第一次為韋斯咸在聯賽杯第二輪的比賽中對[[錫菲聯|錫菲聯]]的比賽以後備球員身份出現在陣容內，但是球會在[[烏普頓公園球場|烏普頓公園球場]]在亙射十二碼球下被撃敗，奧斯科特並沒有上陣<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/28847232|title=BBC Sport — West Ham United 1-1 Sheffield United (4-5 on pens)|work=BBC Sport|accessdate=1 July 2015|archive-date=2015-11-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151125003555/http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/28847232|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.dailymail.co.uk/sport/football/article-2735024/Reece-Oxford-makes-West-Ham-bench-aged-just-15-years-old-Hammers-look-hold-Arsenal-Manchester-United.html|title=Reece Oxford on West Ham bench aged 15 years old amidst Arsenal interest — Daily Mail Online|work=Mail Online|accessdate=1 July 2015|archive-date=2016-03-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160305032711/http://www.dailymail.co.uk/sport/football/article-2735024/Reece-Oxford-makes-West-Ham-bench-aged-just-15-years-old-Hammers-look-hold-Arsenal-Manchester-United.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。奧斯科特仍然是一個青年隊球員，但已吸引了[[車路士|車路士]]、[[阿仙奴|阿仙奴]]和[[曼聯|曼聯]]派出球探觀看他的比賽<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www1.skysports.com/football/news/11685/9546210/transfer-news-west-ham-teenager-reece-oxford-yet-to-agree-professional-contract | title=Transfer news: West Ham teenager Reece Oxford yet to agree professional contract | publisher=ww1.skysports.com | accessdate=4 July 2015 | archive-date=2020-03-19 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200319023849/https://www.skysports.com/football/news/11685/9546210/transfer-news-west-ham-teenager-reece-oxford-yet-to-agree-professional-contract | dead-url=no }}</ref>。2015年1月11日，奧斯科特與韋斯咸簽訂了長期合約<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.thefa.com/news/england/development/2015/jan/england-u17s-captain-reece-oxford-pens-first-pro-deal-at-west-ham-140115|title=England U17s skipper Reece Oxford pens long-term contract with West Ham United on the pitch — England — The FA|author=The Football Association|publisher=|accessdate=1 July 2015|archive-date=2019-06-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190630195504/http://www.thefa.com/news/2015/jan/14/england-u17s-captain-reece-oxford-pens-first-pro-deal-at-west-ham-140115|dead-url=no}}</ref>。在2014-15年賽季的後半段，多次成為韋斯咸在英超比賽中的後備球員，但是並沒有上陣<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/32460283|title=BBC Sport — West Ham United 1-0 Burnley|author=Chris Osborne|work=BBC Sport|accessdate=1 July 2015|archive-date=2015-06-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150625041020/http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/32460283|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/32363168|title=BBC Sport — Queens Park Rangers 0-0 West Ham United|author=Michael Emons|work=BBC Sport|accessdate=1 July 2015|archive-date=2015-07-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150704003325/http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/32363168|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="thefootballassociation">{{cite web|url=http://www.thefa.com/news/england/development/2015/may/west-hams-reece-oxford-aims-to-put-sam-allardyces-lessons-into-practice-with-england-u17s-060515|title=West Ham and England U17s defender Reece Oxford aims to put Big Sam's lessons into practice against Europe's best — England — The FA|author=The Football Association|publisher=|accessdate=1 July 2015|archive-date=2019-06-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190630195459/http://www.thefa.com/news/england/development/2015/may/west-hams-reece-oxford-aims-to-put-sam-allardyces-lessons-into-practice-with-england-u17s-060515|dead-url=no}}</ref>。奧斯科特於2015年5月在球會的球員頒獎晚會中以在青年軍的出色表現獲得了迪倫·湯比迪斯年度大獎成為該年度最佳青年軍球員<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.whufc.com/News/Articles/2015/May/6-May/Oxford-collects-Dylan-Tombides-Award|title=Oxford collects Dylan Tombides Award — West Ham United|publisher=|accessdate=2 July 2015|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150702064510/http://www.whufc.com/News/Articles/2015/May/6-May/Oxford-collects-Dylan-Tombides-Award|archivedate=2015-07-02}}</ref>。

2015年7月2日，奧斯科特取得在16歲首次上陣的機會，以中場球員身份在[[欧足联欧洲联赛|欧洲联赛]]的資格賽第一輪對陣[[安道爾|安道爾]]球會[[盧西塔諾斯足球俱樂部|路施坦奴斯足球會]]的首回合比賽中，主場以3-0取勝。因此他成為了韋斯咸有史以來最年輕的上陣球員<ref name=lusitans1>{{cite news | url=http://www.independent.co.uk/sport/football/european/west-ham-30-lusitans-match-report-diafra-sakho-gives-hammers-winning-start-to-marathon-season-10362711.html | title=West Ham vs Lusitans match report: Diafra Sakho gives Hammers winning start to marathon season | work=The Independent | date=2 July 2015 | accessdate=3 July 2015 | archive-date=2015-09-25 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150925211253/http://www.independent.co.uk/sport/football/european/west-ham-30-lusitans-match-report-diafra-sakho-gives-hammers-winning-start-to-marathon-season-10362711.html | dead-url=no }}</ref>。

==國家隊生涯==
奧斯科特先後效力於英格蘭U16及U17水平的隊伍並於英格蘭在2015年的[[歐洲U-17足球錦標賽|歐洲U-17足球錦標賽]]的比賽中上陣及成為隊長。球隊打至半準決賽，奧斯科特在亙射十二碼球射入協助英格蘭撃敗西班牙取得[[2015年U17世界盃足球賽|2015年U17世界盃足球賽]]的參賽資格<ref>{{cite news|last1=Shergold|first1=Adam|title=England U17 0-0 Spain U17 (Pens 5-3): Young Lions win shootout to qualify for Under 17 World Cup in Chile|url=http://www.dailymail.co.uk/sport/football/article-3088218/England-U17-0-0-Spain-U17-Pens-5-3-Young-Lions-win-shootout-qualify-17-World-Cup-Chile.html|accessdate=4 July 2015|work=[[Daily_Mail|Daily Mail]]|date=19 May 2015|archive-date=2016-03-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160305031412/http://www.dailymail.co.uk/sport/football/article-3088218/England-U17-0-0-Spain-U17-Pens-5-3-Young-Lions-win-shootout-qualify-17-World-Cup-Chile.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

